title: NBA 2K14 v1.14 Android
description:
NBA 2K14 v1.14
Requirements: 4.0+
Overview: NBA 2K14 is the latest installment of the world's biggest and best NBA video game franchise. With more than 38 Sports Game of the Year and "Best Of" mentions last year on console, 2K14 is set to rule the virtual hardwood on iOS. This year, we've joined forces with the league's most dominant force: LeBron James. NBA 2K14 will raise the bar, yet again.
Image

Image
Product Features
-Multiplayer: Take the court against your friends via Bluetooth.
-Intuitive Controls: Choose between classic control and One-Finger control, built specifically for mobile devices.
-Multiseason Mode: Play through multiple NBA seasons and establish your team as a dynasty.
-Full 2K Beats soundtrack
